{"tid":147610,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"除非上到公屋, 如果唔係租緊樓果啲先係真「樓奴」","createTime":"2017-03-08T03:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T06:16:28.000Z","uid":58319,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e29d9553cd29ed452f2e22eea278b363fd7317d8","tid":147610,"uid":58319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"供樓有7成自己袋落袋d錢，30年後就算一毫子都吾值，但起碼自己同仔女都有個家，租樓就全數比業主，30年後人地就擁有一層樓，你自己呢？你可以講首期難比，但吾好成日講(樓奴)，租樓既人先係真正既樓奴，除非你住公屋啦"},{"pid":"ff3ef633eaf74ab43cdc43527f0f221043fed53a","tid":147610,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:50:12.000Z","msg":"哦, 你講完之後想表演d咩"},{"pid":"e54a92537a9c52b87e6ecdcb4a383b9f571c0dc2","tid":147610,"uid":14491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"吾你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa122017a66820bb4bfaf439db06995e3b850f9","tid":147610,"uid":73677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吾你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吾你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b11f873f1fe703c58afe0c223eca4791111fd7","tid":147610,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都on9<br />\n<br />\n當樓價開始唔值錢果陣租金係一定會相對降低<br />\n但你還俾銀行果筆錢係唔會少左<br />\n即係係樓市低迷果陣你仲要拎一舊錢出黎還俾銀行<br />\n<br />\n至於點解會唔值錢大多數因為需求降低<br />\n需求降低果陣你有個物業根本就冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9c9aa72f3173c25ae10ac0e76a84263d296d51","tid":147610,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吾你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吾你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/no